import * as React from 'react';
import {NavigationContainer} from '@react-navigation/native';
import {createStackNavigator,TransitionPresets,CardStyleInterpolators,HeaderStyleInterpolators} from  '@react-navigation/stack';
import { View, Text } from 'react-native';
import { fromLeft, zoomIn, zoomOut } from 'react-navigation-transitions'
import { createDrawerNavigator } from '@react-navigation/drawer';
import SignUp from '../screens/SignUp';
import Login from '../screens/Login';
import araba from '../screens/araba';
import forgot from'../screens/forgot';
import iücotoparkalanlar from '../screens/DinamikButton/iücotoparkalanlar';
import timer from '../screens/timer'
import homepage from '../screens/homepage'
import drawer from '../screens/drawer'

//İSTANBUL
import mapIst from '../screens/Cities/İstanbul/mapIst'
import istGezilecek from '../screens/Cities/İstanbul/istGezilecek';
import listeIst from '../screens/Cities/İstanbul/listeIst'

import galataTower from'../screens/Cities/İstanbul/GalataTower/galataTower'
import galataTowerInfo from'../screens/Cities/İstanbul/GalataTower/galataTowerInfo'

import Ayasofya from '../screens/Cities/İstanbul/Ayasofya/Ayasofya'
import AyasofyaInfo from '../screens/Cities/İstanbul/Ayasofya/AyasofyaInfo'

 import Sultanahmet from '../screens/Cities/İstanbul/Sultanahmet/Sultanahmet'
 import SultanahmetInfo from '../screens/Cities/İstanbul/Sultanahmet/SultanahmetInfo'

 import Topkapi from '../screens/Cities/İstanbul/TopkapiPalace/Topkapi'
 import TopkapiInfo from '../screens/Cities/İstanbul/TopkapiPalace/TopkapiInfo'

 //ANKARA
 import mapAnk from '../screens/Cities/Ankara/mapAnk'
 import ankGezilecek from '../screens/Cities/Ankara/ankGezilecek';
 import listeAnk from '../screens/Cities/Ankara/listeAnk'

import Anitkabir from '../screens/Cities/Ankara/Anıtkabir/Anitkabir'
import AnitkabirInfo from '../screens/Cities/Ankara/Anıtkabir/AnitkabirInfo'

import AnkaraKalesi from '../screens/Cities/Ankara/AnkaraKalesi/AnkaraKalesi'
import AnkaraKalesiInfo from '../screens/Cities/Ankara/AnkaraKalesi/AnkaraKalesiInfo'

import Etnografya from '../screens/Cities/Ankara/Etnografya/Etnografya'
import EtnografyaInfo from '../screens/Cities/Ankara/Etnografya/EtnografyaInfo'

import AnadoluMedeniyetler from '../screens/Cities/Ankara/AnadoluMedeniyetler/AnadoluMedeniyetler'
import AnadoluMedeniyetlerInfo from '../screens/Cities/Ankara/AnadoluMedeniyetler/AnadoluMedeniyetlerInfo'


const Stack = createStackNavigator();

const Drawer = createDrawerNavigator();



const Navigation = props => {
    return (
      
     
      
      
        
        
     
            <Stack.Navigator >
                <Stack.Screen name="Login" component={Login} options={{headerShown: false,...TransitionPresets.RevealFromBottomAndroid}} />
                <Stack.Screen name="SignUp" component={SignUp} options={{headerShown: false,...TransitionPresets.RevealFromBottomAndroid}} />
                <Stack.Screen name="araba" component={araba} options={{headerShown: false,  ...TransitionPresets.RevealFromBottomAndroid}} />
                <Stack.Screen name="forgot" component={forgot} options={{headerShown: false, ...TransitionPresets.RevealFromBottomAndroid}} />
                <Stack.Screen name="iücotoparkalanlar" component={iücotoparkalanlar} options={{headerShown: false,...TransitionPresets.RevealFromBottomAndroid}} />
                <Stack.Screen name="timer" component={timer} options={{headerShown: false,...TransitionPresets.RevealFromBottomAndroid}} />
                <Stack.Screen name="homepage" component={homepage} options={{headerShown: false,...TransitionPresets.RevealFromBottomAndroid}} />
                <Stack.Screen name="drawer" component={drawer} options={{headerShown: false,...TransitionPresets.SlideFromRightIOS}} />


                <Stack.Screen name="mapIst" component={mapIst} options={{headerShown: false,...TransitionPresets.SlideFromRightIOS}} />
                <Stack.Screen name="istGezilecek" component={istGezilecek} options={{headerShown: false,...TransitionPresets.RevealFromBottomAndroid}} />
                <Stack.Screen name="listeIst" component={listeIst} options={{headerShown: false,...TransitionPresets.RevealFromBottomAndroid}} />
               
                <Stack.Screen name="galataTower" component={galataTower} options={{headerShown: false,...TransitionPresets.SlideFromRightIOS}} />
                <Stack.Screen name="galataTowerInfo" component={galataTowerInfo} options={{headerShown: false,...TransitionPresets.SlideFromRightIOS}} />
                <Stack.Screen name="Ayasofya" component={Ayasofya} options={{headerShown: false,...TransitionPresets.SlideFromRightIOS}} />
                <Stack.Screen name="AyasofyaInfo" component={AyasofyaInfo} options={{headerShown: false,...TransitionPresets.SlideFromRightIOS}} />
                <Stack.Screen name="Sultanahmet" component={Sultanahmet} options={{headerShown: false,...TransitionPresets.SlideFromRightIOS}} />
                <Stack.Screen name="SultanahmetInfo" component={SultanahmetInfo} options={{headerShown: false,...TransitionPresets.SlideFromRightIOS}} />
                <Stack.Screen name="Topkapi" component={Topkapi} options={{headerShown: false,...TransitionPresets.SlideFromRightIOS}} />
                <Stack.Screen name="TopkapiInfo" component={TopkapiInfo} options={{headerShown: false,...TransitionPresets.SlideFromRightIOS}} />


               <Stack.Screen name="mapAnk" component={mapAnk} options={{headerShown: false,...TransitionPresets.SlideFromRightIOS}} />
               <Stack.Screen name="ankGezilecek" component={ankGezilecek} options={{headerShown: false,...TransitionPresets.RevealFromBottomAndroid}} />
               <Stack.Screen name="listeAnk" component={listeAnk} options={{headerShown: false,...TransitionPresets.RevealFromBottomAndroid}} />


               <Stack.Screen name="Anitkabir" component={Anitkabir} options={{headerShown: false,...TransitionPresets.SlideFromRightIOS}} />
               <Stack.Screen name="AnkaraKalesi" component={AnkaraKalesi} options={{headerShown: false,...TransitionPresets.SlideFromRightIOS}} />
               <Stack.Screen name="Etnografya" component={Etnografya} options={{headerShown: false,...TransitionPresets.SlideFromRightIOS}} />
               <Stack.Screen name="AnadoluMedeniyetler" component={AnadoluMedeniyetler} options={{headerShown: false,...TransitionPresets.SlideFromRightIOS}} />
               <Stack.Screen name="AnitkabirInfo" component={AnitkabirInfo} options={{headerShown: false,...TransitionPresets.SlideFromRightIOS}} />
               <Stack.Screen name="AnkaraKalesiInfo" component={AnkaraKalesiInfo} options={{headerShown: false,...TransitionPresets.SlideFromRightIOS}} />
               <Stack.Screen name="EtnografyaInfo" component={EtnografyaInfo} options={{headerShown: false,...TransitionPresets.SlideFromRightIOS}} />
               <Stack.Screen name="AnadoluMedeniyetlerInfo" component={AnadoluMedeniyetlerInfo} options={{headerShown: false,...TransitionPresets.SlideFromRightIOS}} />
 

               
            </Stack.Navigator>

   
    );
    
};



export {Navigation};
